data.description: Price Improvement and BROKER BONUS!! Welcome to your future home.. This lovely home has several upgrades. HVAC, Furnace is less than 1 year since replaced. Stainless Steel appliances. New insulated garage doors. Bathrooms have been updated. Updated lighting throughout the home with a retractable ceiling fan.  There are 3 bedrooms and 2 baths upstairs. The Basement showcases a nice rec room/lounge or 4th bedroom with a full bath. There is a relaxing deck overlooking the large fenced in serene backyard with a nice sized gazebo to enjoy all your family gatherings. This is a great opportunity for a first time home buyer or an investor looking to expand their portfolio. This is the House waiting for the right buyers. Just 10 mins from 75 N/S and easy access to the express lane. Schedule a showing today and tour this exceptional property! By Appointment only. Please allow a 24 hour notice. Home is homeowner occupied.
